summary: This Mod adds a new island to explore with 3 Dungeons and a player home.
descriptionHtml:
This mod is my first mod and adds a new island, Oceans Rest, to the game with its own npcs and vendors as well as Two new dungeons.The ship that takes you there is in the solitude docks and there are two new merchants to buy thing off of, Dro'Barri and Chaluree.

Explore the volskegger ruins a burial crypt bound to give you a challenge. in Frothgirs bane You will stumble across An ancient artefact, the lost mask of the ancient nords.
Also two new NPCs in town, Fisovius and Nararuth.

Includes a tunnel To oceans rest depths and A new Cave That leads to The catacombs Of oceans rests' Former citizens.

A new dungeon that will take you to Fargenhime where your reward for completing it will be found, your new house! Enjoy and please feed back to me if you find any bugs in the mod.
author: Damarkster5
